<P>
   SCI-HURRICANE (Boston) -- Sixty years ago New England was
clobbered by one of the most devastating hurricanes in history. It
was because of that storm that hurricane research and forecasting
began in earnest. By David L. Chanlder. (2 takes)
</P>
<P>
