   WHEN TO GO:
</P>
<P>
   Jamaica is a year-round destination, although the peak season,
when hotel prices are higher, is between mid-December and
mid-April. It's hot in the summer, but you'll get better bargains
by traveling then.
</P>
<P>
   HOW TO TRAVEL:
</P>
<P>
   From the United States, Air Jamaica serves both Montego Bay and
Kingston from U.S. gateways that include Atlanta, Chicago and
