<P>
   ``You can see the people here,'' said one young Kuwaiti man,
gesturing around a crowded mall that boasts stores by Laura Ashley,
Godiva and Gucci. ``How many people are carrying (shopping) bags?
They are just walking around!''
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
</P>
<P>
   Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
</P>
