<P>
   WINE-TALK (UNdated) _ So you're a wine fanatic whose day is
incomplete if it doesn't include a bottle of some rare California
cabernet. Unfortunately, you have lots of incomplete days, because
most shops don't carry them and those that do are always sold out.
Help is at hand. First Sip, a new monthly wine newsletter, not only
identifies the wines, as do all the other newsletters, but goes the
extra mile and lists where to find them. By Frank J. Prial.
