</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980908.0161 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-08 16:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3970 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-OPTIONS-HNS     09-08 0036
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-OPTIONS-HNS </SLUG>
  
 Tuesday, Sept. 9, 1998 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; Editors: &LR;  &QC;
