<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-08 17:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4221 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CHILE-FILM-REVIEW-NYT     09-08 0687
