dozens of functions on the big MD-11 showed system after system
breaking down, the chief investigator said this evening. With
enough analysis, the recorder may disclose where the plane's
problem began. By Matthew L. Wald. (The story has moved in ``a''
news file; see 1stLd-Writethru.)
