<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EDIT-MCGWIRE-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORIAL: MCGWIRE DOES IT! 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also moving in ``k'' news file.) 
(th) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
