</P>
<P>
   49. Aug. 20 at Cleveland Jim Perry
</P>
<P>
   50. Aug. 22 at Los Angeles Ken McBride
</P>
<P>
   51. Aug. 26 at Kansas City Jerry Walker
</P>
<P>
   52. Sept. 2 Detroit Frank Lary
</P>
<P>
   53. Sept. 2 Detroit Hank Aguirre
</P>
<P>
   54. Sept. 6 Washington Tom Cheney
</P>
<P>
   55. Sept. 7 Cleveland Dick Stigman
</P>
<P>
   56. Sept. 9 Cleveland Mudcat Grant
</P>
<P>
   57. Sept. 16 at Detroit Frank Lary
</P>
<P>
   58. Sept. 17 at Detroit Terry Fox
</P>
