<HEADLINE>
SOSA SHOWS RESPECT; MCGWIRE RETURNS IT 
</HEADLINE>
  (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also moving in ``s'' news file.) 
(th) 
 By JACK CURRY    
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
