A4885 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBN-MCGWIRE-62-COX     09-08 0235
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BBN-MCGWIRE-62-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    McGwire makes home run history
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving in (a) general news and (s) sports categories.)
 &HT;    By I.J. Rosenberg
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ST. LOUIS _ On a dreamy night in a steamy baseball city, the
sport whose tradition is built largely on numbers introduced
perhaps its grandest Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
   No. 62.
</P>
